{"tid":2143852,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中央打救香港？用兩個字，就可以化解港共PR","createTime":"2020-08-07T10:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T11:04:11.000Z","uid":70786,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"69f2769235ce553dca54d4037d24364601779740","tid":2143852,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">贖罪</span></strong></span><br />\n支那檢測人員唔係咩馳援香港（遲緩就有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n支那派人落嚟做大規模檢測<br />\n係要為散播武漢肺炎贖罪<br />\n<br />\n同D中立/淺藍撚講<br />\n唔係中國政府封鎖武漢不力搞到全球大爆發<br />\n唔係林鄭唔封關仲開個漏洞將香港變無掩雞籠<br />\n你今日要俾人插鼻？<br />\n武漢肺炎至今已經奪去四十幾位香港人性命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全球死70萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人係唔會因為搞免費檢測就原諒佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：強制我都唔撚會驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c048d93c5162dc2c1c91cd570bc588ab23ad91ba","tid":2143852,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"大家一定要堅持叫武漢肺炎<br />\n只要呢個稱呼深植所有人心入面<br />\n支那就洗脫唔到罪孽<br />\n想改寫歷史？收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10b8786ec72634660c828440806d99cb2d8ccb0","tid":2143852,"uid":55493,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"你就真係PR啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑都畀你講到變白<br />\n搞死你變贖罪"},{"pid":"8e89dfa30715e470a8e80e92cbc3b5b93b9ad05b","tid":2143852,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b10b8786ec72634660c828440806d99cb2d8ccb0","tid":2143852,"uid":55493,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"你就真係PR啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑都畀你講到變白<br />\n搞死你變贖罪"},"citedBy":0,"